title: Motley Fool Money: 03.13.2009
description: What happened on Wall Street to make the stock market actually go up this week?  How good was the news coming out of Citigroup and Bank of America?  And with layoffs hitting Sesame Street, which Muppets will be getting pink slips?  We answer these burning questions, share a few beefs, and reveal some of the stocks on our radar in this week’s edition of Motley Fool Money.
